{"tid":388550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓逼遷平壤低下層居民 確保首都特權階級食物配給穩定","createTime":"2017-09-05T14:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T14:51:26.000Z","uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b75f12e64c993c6d4842ed1d7e61c3ee5d792ea","tid":388550,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T14:01:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170905/1197148/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170905%2F1197148%2F&d=03AktAJquTfWmOz0pf1dJm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=efe4b302\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170905/1197148/</a><br />\n<br />\n北韓近年夏季出現旱災，加上國際強化制裁導致當地食物短缺，首都平壤已大受影響。消息人士透露，勞動黨為避免首都因食物不足，影響政權穩定，已下令部份平民離開平壤，以減少首都人口。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台（Radio Free Asia）引述北韓消息指，平壤如今的人口估計有260萬人，比2010年的300萬人少，而北韓政權已要求，要把人口降至200萬，方法包括：迫使有前科的人及失業人士遷離平壤。<br />\n<br />\n迫遷政策是由北韓勞動黨決定，再由平壤市政委員會實施，旨在確保平壤特權階層的食物配給穩定。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"66ad8c9351516f3e8ee5ae4bdf9980237b7c5ce2","tid":388550,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae81a1bab2ceda178008d3b3cca685f6396f77f","tid":388550,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"其實生活係 北韓偏遠農村, 可能會更好<br />\n<br />\n最起碼監控無咁嚴, 可以自己種食物, 自己食<br />\n<br />\n住係平壤, 雖然係特權階級, 但同一時間受到嚴密監控........仲要靠政府配給食物"},{"pid":"b9dbf19d77b129213eb14b9305510b13c85dafb8","tid":388550,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實生活係 北韓偏遠農村, 可能會更好<br />\n<br />\n最起碼監控無咁嚴, 可以自己種食物, 自己食<br />\n<br />\n住係平壤, 雖然係特權階級, 但同一時間受到嚴密監控........仲要靠政府配給食物</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/North_Korean_famine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNorth_Korean_famine&d=03AktAJquTfWmOz0pf1dJm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=bdd93209\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/North_Korean_famine</a>"},{"pid":"5bf635da0b6e6c1dccb0e757d51ca85256c78e0b","tid":388550,"uid":68203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T14:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實生活係 北韓偏遠農村, 可能會更好<br />\n<br />\n<strong>]最起碼監控無咁嚴, 可以自己種食物, 自己食</strong><br />\n<br />\n住係平壤, 雖然係特權階級, 但同一時間受到嚴密監控........仲要靠政府配給食物</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />證明你唔太清楚究竟大躍進同埋蘇聯大饑荒係咩一回事"}]}